<div class="content-container">
    <form id="forget_pass_form" class="loginForm" action="https://srcpjcc.clubautomation.com/index/forgetpass" method="post">
        To reset your password, please enter the email address associated with your account
        <input type="hidden" name="dosubmit" value="submit"/>
        <div class="input-wrapper">
            <div class="input-border">
                <input name="email" type="text" value="Email" onblur="onBlurAlphaBox(this, 'Email')" onfocus="onFocusAlphaBox(this, 'Email')" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="error"></div>
        <div class="buttons-group">
            <div class="buttons-group-wrapper">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn-small float" onclick="doForgetPassword()">Submit</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn-small float" onclick="Windows.close(modalWin.getId());">Cancel</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
    <script type="text/javascript">
    function doForgetPassword()
    {
        var url = '/index/forgetpass';
        var eventId = $j('body').data('signUpEvent') || 0;
        var scheduleId = $j('body').data('signUpSchedule') || 0;
                        
        url += '?selected-event-id=' + eventId + '&selected-schedule-id=' + scheduleId;
        
        doAjax('forget_pass_form', url, null, 'onEmailSend(response)');
    }
    
    function onEmailSend(response)
    {
        var data = response.responseJSON;

        if (data.forget_error) {
            $j("#forget_pass_form .error").html(data.forget_error);
            $j("#forget_pass_form .input-wrapper").addClass('error-field');
            Windows.getFocusedWindow().updateHeight();
        } else if (data.msg) {
            Windows.close(modalWin.getId());
            $j("#success-description").html(data.msg);
            showModalForm('Forgot my Password', $('found_email'), 366, 140, true, {className:'alphacubeCpacNew', closable: false}, true);
        }
    }
    </script>
</div>
    </div>

<div id="forcing_change_password" style="display:none">
    <div class="content-container alphacubeCpacNew_popup_success">
        <div class="info-message">
        </div>
        <div class="buttons-group">
            <div class="buttons-group-wrapper">
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="btn-small float" id="fnc-reset-password-link-btn">OK</a>
            </div>
        </div>

<script type="text/javascript">
$j(document).ready(function() {
    $j('body').on('focus', '.content-container input', function() {
        var self = $j(this);
        self.closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('active-field').removeClass('error-field');
        if (self.attr('type') == 'password') {
            return true;
        }
        var label = self.parent().find('.input-label').val();
        if (self.val() == label) {
            self.val('');
            if (self.attr('id') == 'password-text') {
                self.hide();
                self.parent().find('[type=password]').val('').show().focus();
            }
        }
    });
    $j('body').on('blur', '.content-container input', function() {
        var self = $j(this);
        var label = self.parent().find('.input-label').val();
        self.closest('.input-wrapper').removeClass('active-field');
        if (self.val().length == 0) {
            if (self.attr('type') == 'password') {
                self.hide();
                self.parent().find('[type=text]').show().val(label);
            } else {
                self.val(label);
            }
        }
    });
    $j('body').on('click', '#forgot-your-password', function() {
        showModalForm('Forgot my Password', $('forgot_password'), 366, 210, true, {className:'alphacubeCpacNew', closable: false}, true);
        return false;
    });
    $j('body').on('click', '#login-button', function() {
        $j.getScript('/public/scripts/jquery.form.min.js', function() {
            showAjaxStarted();
            $j('#login-form').ajaxSubmit({
                beforeSubmit : function(array, form, options) {
                    var login = $j('#login');
                    var password = $j('#password');
                    var isValid = true;
                    if (login.val() == 'Email' || login.val().length == 0) {
                        login.closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('error-field');
                        isValid = false;
                    }
                    if (password.val().length == 0) {
                        password.closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('error-field');
                        isValid = false;
                    }
                    if(!isValid) {
                        showAjaxFinished();
                    }

                    return isValid;
                },
                success : function(response) {
                    showAjaxFinished();
                    if (response.status == 1 || response.status == 2) {
                        var url = response.status == 2 ? response.redirect_to : '/calendar/event-info';
                        var id = $j('body').data('signUpId') || 0;
                        var eventId = $j('body').data('signUpEvent') || 0;
                        var scheduleId = $j('body').data('signUpSchedule') || 0;
                        
                        if (id) {
                            if (scheduleId) {
                                url += '?id=' + id + '&selected-schedule-id=' + scheduleId;
                            } else if (eventId) {
                                url += '?id=' + id + '&selected-event-id=' + eventId;
                            }
                        } else {
                            url += '?id=' + eventId + '&selected-schedule-id=' + scheduleId;
                        }
                            
                        window.location.href = url;
                    } else if(response.status == 3 && response.forcing_change_password){
                        $j('#forcing_change_password .info-message').append('<span>'+response.forcing_change_password+'</span>');
                        $j('#fnc-reset-password-link-btn').attr('href', response.change_password_link);
                        showModalForm('Password Update', $('forcing_change_password'), 366, 120, true, {className:'alphacubeCpacNew2', closable: true}, true);
                    } else {
                        $j('#login, #password').closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('error-field');
                        
                        if (response.message) {
                            $j('#login-form .error').html(response.message);
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
        });
        return false;
    });
    $j('body').on('click', '#search-button', function() {
        $j.getScript('/public/scripts/jquery.form.min.js', function() {
            var signUpEvent = $j('body').data('signUpEvent') || 0;
            var signUpSchedule = $j('body').data('signUpSchedule') || 0;
            var type = $j('body').data('signUpType');

            $j('#search-account-form').ajaxSubmit({
                beforeSerialize : function(form, options) {
                    $j.each($j('#search-account-form [type=text]'), function(k, v){
                        var textField = $j(v);
                        var hiddenFild = textField.parent().find('.input-label');
                        if (textField.val() == hiddenFild.val()) {
                            textField.val('');
                        }
                    });
                    return true;
                },
                data : {
                    'selected-event-id': signUpEvent,
                    'selected-schedule-id': signUpSchedule,
                    'type': type
                },
                beforeSubmit : function(array, form, options) {
                    $j('.errors-container').html('');
                    $j('.find-account [type=text]').closest('.input-wrapper').removeClass('error-field');
                    isValid = true;

                    var email = $j('#email');
                    var firstName = $j('#first-name');
                    var lastName = $j('#last-name');
                    if (email.val().length == 0 && firstName.val().length == 0 && lastName.val().length == 0) {
                        email.closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('error-field');
                        isValid = false;
                    }

                    if (isValid) {
                        showAjaxStarted();
                    }

                    return isValid;
                },
                success : function(response) {
                    showAjaxFinished();
                    if (response.error != undefined) {
                        if (response.step == 2) {
                            $j('#errors-container-step-2').html(response.error);
                        } else { 
                            $j('#errors-container').html(response.error);
                        }
                        $j("#step").val(2);
                        $j('.find-account [type=text]').trigger('blur').closest('.input-wrapper').addClass('error-field');
                        $j('#additional-search-fieds').show();
                        
                        var dialog = $j('.dialog');
                        dialog.height(650).css('top', ($j(window).height() - 650) / 2 + $j(window).scrollTop());
                        dialog.find('div.alphacubeCpacNew_content').height(550);
                        dialog.find('.account-access').height(550);
                    } else if (response.msg != undefined) {
                        $j('#success-description').html(response.msg);
                        showModalForm('Forgot my Password', $('success-dialog'), 366, 150, true, {className:'alphacubeCpacNew', closable: false}, true);
                    } else if (response.link) {
                        window.location = response.link; 
                    }
                }
            });
        });
        return false;
    });
    $j('body').on('click', '#create-profile-link', function() {
        var signUpEvent = $j('body').data('signUpEvent') || 0;
        var signUpSchedule = $j('body').data('signUpSchedule') || 0;

        var url = '/profile/create?selected-event-id=' + signUpEvent + '&selected-schedule-id=' + signUpSchedule;

        var type = $j('body').data('signUpType');
        if (type == 'group-activity') {
            url += '&type=group-activity';
        }

        $j(this).attr('href', url);

        return true;
    });
});
</script></div>
<script type="text/javascript">
    (function($) {
        $(function() {
            $('body').caEventSignUpPopup({"userId":null});
            
                    });
    })(jQuery);
</script>

    </div>
